{
  "stem": "19895.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Molina was the one who came forward, and telephone communications in the city were almost not for private [INAUDIBLE], just like before the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Private people didn't have too many telephones, if any.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he is knocking on our door where he found us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He knew that we were living in the neighborhood again, but not in the location where the building was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my father, after the war, made contact with him and so on, or maybe wanted to get his shoes fixed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So he says, Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Lichtmann-- and he knew I was already back-- he says your wife, your mother wrote a letter from Sweden to us, Mr.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Molina, care of.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in the letter, he's asking, he wants-- she wants to know if you people are alive or if I would know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was hoping that this contact might clear her curiosity, and then hopes that you are, if I know anything about you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So why don't you answer?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why don't you answer?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in a couple of weeks, we got a letter to our address.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And mail between countries started to develop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I returned to finish high school education, which is another story again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And mother said that she's in Sweden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Swedish [INAUDIBLE] took her from Bergen-Belsen She was in the famous, infamous Bergen-Belsen concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was turned away from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Auschwitz they were almost at the gates of Auschwitz, and Auschwitz didn't take them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were turned off and taken to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where she survived in terribly, miserable physical shape.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then in Sweden, the Swedish [INAUDIBLE] placed her in a hospital and built her up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was already having a job in Sweden and working.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
